Class JobLauncherExecutionDriver.Launcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.job_exec.JobLauncherExecutionDriver.Launcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Instrumentable, GobblinInstanceEnvironment, JobExecutionLauncher
    Enclosing class:
    JobLauncherExecutionDriver

    public static class JobLauncherExecutionDriver.Launcher
extends Object
implements JobExecutionLauncher, GobblinInstanceEnvironment
    Creates a new instance of JobLauncherExecutionDriver.

    Conventions

    • If no jobLauncherType is specified, one will be determined by the JobSpec (see {@link JobLauncherFactory).
    • Convention for sysConfig: use the sysConfig of the gobblinInstance if specified, otherwise use empty config.
    • Convention for log: use gobblinInstance logger plus "." + jobSpec if specified, otherwise use JobExecutionDriver class name plus "." + jobSpec
